      "date": "2014-10-23 18:05:52.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/7e5d6914-5ade-11e4-b6be-5254006e85c2).  Ran 7 tests.  No failures.",
