    {
      "id": "d5cce3a3c15904749b6d05e0db56fd653b26d8e8",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 251,
        "name": "Bob Glossman",
        "email": "bob.glossman@intel.com",
        "username": "bogl",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2014-10-23 18:29:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\ndon't think that the autoconf check is trying to distinguish RHEL from other distros, it's looking for scripts that the lustre init scripts look for and use.  since the init scripts won't operate unless these other scripts are there the init scripts are left out if not there.\n\ndoesn't make sense to me to install scripts that can't be used.\n\nI didn't put this check in, but it seems reasonable.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "96a08f3ecaa06663ddbfc8f2caf9d168b56a48fb",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 109,
        "name": "Christopher J. Morrone",
        "email": "morrone2@llnl.gov",
        "username": "morrone"
      },
      "date": "2014-10-23 18:34:40.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe check is not reasonable because it results in missing RHEL init scripts on RHEL servers when Lustre is built under mock.  The old init script status quo is much preferable to the present outright broken package.\n\nPlease see the jira ticket.  We can have a conversation there if the problem description is not clear.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "fe4a97628a4912a8c1381c128ba494bd12876cb7",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 109,
        "name": "Christopher J. Morrone",
        "email": "morrone2@llnl.gov",
        "username": "morrone"
      },
      "date": "2014-10-23 18:38:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nThe LU-4707 patch also introduced the following two shell conditionals that also need to be removed in this patch:\n\nif [ -f $RPM_BUILD_ROOT%{_sysconfdir}/init.d/lustre ]; then\n\nif [ -f $RPM_BUILD_ROOT%{_sysconfdir}/init.d/lnet ]; then",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
